Erste Bank Hungary, EBRD Sign 15 Million-Euro Loan Agreement

-- B y   E d i t h   B a l a z s
-- 
2011-05-23T07:53:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-23/erste-bank-hungary-ebrd-sign-15-million-euro-loan-agreement.html
The European Bank for Reconstruction
and Development will lend the Hungarian unit of Erste Bank AG 15
million euros ($21 million) to finance energy-efficiency
investments.  Interest rates  on the EBRD loan are market-based and the
money will be extended to local councils, Janos Major, deputy
chief executive officer for corporate finance at Erste Bank
Hungary Zrt., said at a press conference today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Edith Balazs in Budapest at 
 ebalazs1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Gomez at   jagomez@bloomberg.net  